SIMPLE: advanced
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Advanced
<hw>Ad*vanced"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In
the van or front.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In the front or before others, as regards progress
or ideas; <as>as, <ex>advanced</ex> opinions, <ex>advanced</ex>
thinkers</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Far on in life or time.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A gentleman <qex>advanced</qex> in years, with a hard experience
written in his wrinkles.</q> <rj><qau>Hawthorne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Advanced guard</b></col>, <cd>a detachment of troops
which precedes the march of the main body.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Advancement</ent>⟦br⟧
